{"tid":2201003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【白羅斯】蒙面警將數十婦女擄走 示威者怒扯防暴面罩要見樣","createTime":"2020-09-13T12:19:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T14:12:47.000Z","uid":227801,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"93ba6c506086a861b055d0d7c141c52a60e6d180","tid":2201003,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:19:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200913/GZOYDVL575DURINIKFW755JGRM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200913%2FGZOYDVL575DURINIKFW755JGRM%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8N8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=a3ce67bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200913%2FGZOYDVL575DURINIKFW755JGRM%2F&h=bc7e4047\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200913/GZOYDVL575DURINIKFW755JGRM/</a><br />\n白羅斯首都明斯克繼續爆發反政府示威，數十名和平請願的婦女被防暴警察拘捕，親反對派媒體表示，2名記者也被警方扣留。<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯群眾為了抗議警暴和現任總統盧卡申科（Alexander Lukashenko）選舉舞弊，計劃星期日（13日）在明斯克舉行大規模遊行。在主要遊行開始前，幾十名婦女周六先在市中心集結，部份人高叫口號，要求政府釋放被捕的反對派領袖科列斯尼科娃（Maria Kolesnikova）。當隊伍走到市內的自由廣場時，數十名戴著黑色面罩的男子突然衝出，嘗試拘捕示威婦女。獨立媒體拍攝的片段也顯示，防暴警察將多名婦女拋上印有警方標誌的客貨車。<br />\n<br />\n設在波蘭的反對派電視台「白羅斯衞星」（Belsat）也表示，在現場採訪的2名記者同樣被扣留。<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯內政部發言人回應事件時，只證實「多名女子被拘捕」，但沒有公開具體人數，也沒有解釋任何詳情。<br />\n白羅斯這次動盪期間，在位26年的盧卡申科正面臨嚴峻的政治挑戰。他周一（14日）將於索契與俄羅斯總統普京會面，討論進一步拉近兩國關係的事宜。<br />\n法新社"},{"pid":"30f9aa5a4412e6263eea193b37fdd81e80d4dd09","tid":2201003,"uid":282352,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6315d9eac7a474fc579183eb926402fc7584dd25","tid":2201003,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6111cc33cfd0a5e892e3cbeedaf95a788a627f96","tid":2201003,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:30:04.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑"},{"pid":"78b04a94884e9fbbbfa4758304cba913047918ff","tid":2201003,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"軍警叛變 <br />\n其中一個好重要的因素係<br />\n軍民覺得反抗者會贏<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯表態支持後 <br />\n盧卡申科穩住左國內勢力"},{"pid":"ccab06da0e42f8a5c4c17b01a6b6a61d8620ad11","tid":2201003,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78b04a94884e9fbbbfa4758304cba913047918ff","tid":2201003,"uid":191926,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:34:00.000Z","msg":"軍警叛變 <br />\n其中一個好重要的因素係<br />\n軍民覺得反抗者會贏<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯表態支持後 <br />\n盧卡申科穩住左國內勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"香港黑警唔叛變 <br />\n其中一個原因係佢地從來都唔覺得我地會贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歷史上女武神行動<br />\n好多人忽視左背景 <br />\n十幾日前盟軍成功係諾曼第登陸"},{"pid":"4b3725902f64173f0c24b72c3e9642e13d859818","tid":2201003,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"邊忽話軍警叛變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926c41b458b0bdd5ec9e339a99963b1deb2ce76c","tid":2201003,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3725902f64173f0c24b72c3e9642e13d859818","tid":2201003,"uid":653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"邊忽話軍警叛變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"可能有小部分放大報導"},{"pid":"ac2983eff2f90bbb551b5db4ee3a07851ded6a08","tid":2201003,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T14:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4f1865c012b5331c8fed9a9c2ccc0ff17d2f6b","tid":2201003,"uid":3752